<div class="relative bg-gray-800 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="hidden sm:block sm:absolute sm:inset-0">
    <svg class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 transform translate-x-1/2 mb-48 text-gray-700 lg:top-0 lg:mt-28 lg:mb-0 xl:transform-none xl:translate-x-0" width="364" height="384" viewBox="0 0 364 384" fill="none">
      <defs>
        <pattern id="eab71dd9-9d7a-47bd-8044-256344ee00d0" x="0" y="0" width="20" height="20" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
          <rect x="0" y="0" width="4" height="4" fill="currentColor" />
        </pattern>
      </defs>
      <rect width="364" height="384" fill="url(#eab71dd9-9d7a-47bd-8044-256344ee00d0)" />
    </svg>
  </div>
  <% flash.each do |type, msg| %>
    <div>
      <%= msg %>
    </div>
  <% end %>

  <div class="relative pt-6 pb-12 sm:pb-32">
    <main class="mt-8 sm:mt-16 md:mt-20 lg:mt-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl">
        <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-8">
          <div class="px-4 sm:px-6 sm:text-center md:max-w-2xl md:mx-auto lg:col-span-6 lg:text-left lg:flex lg:items-center">
            <div>
              <h2 class="mt-4 text-4xl tracking-tight leading-10 font-extrabold text-white sm:mt-5 sm:leading-none sm:text-6xl lg:mt-6 lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl">
                Letter Legal Page Separator
                <br class="hidden md:inline">
                <span class="text-indigo-400">Fast. Secure. Free.</span>
              </h2>
              <p class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-300 sm:mt-5 sm:text-xl lg:text-lg xl:text-xl">
                Sort a PDF document containing mixed letter and legal pages into two separate piles - one for letter, one for legal.
              </p>

              <p class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-300 sm:mt-5 sm:text-xl lg:text-lg xl:text-xl">
                Just drop your file in and click "Separate my PDF". We never keep your file.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-12 sm:mt-16 lg:mt-0 lg:col-span-6">
            <div class="bg-white sm:max-w-md sm:w-full sm:mx-auto sm:rounded-lg sm:overflow-hidden">
              <div class="px-4 py-8 sm:px-10">
                <div>
                  <%= render 'uploads/form', upload: @upload %>
                </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="lg:text-center">
      <h3 class="mt-2 text-3xl leading-8 font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl sm:leading-10">
        A free product from
        <a href="https://orequals.com">
          <img src="https://orequals.com/img/or-equals-logo.png" alt="Or Equals" class="h-12 inline">
        </a>
      </h3>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-xl leading-7 text-gray-500 lg:mx-auto">
        We have extensive experience with building software for the legal field.
        <a href="https://orequals.com">
          Check us out!
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto pt-12 pb-16 sm:pt-16 sm:pb-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:pt-20 lg:pb-28 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-3xl leading-9 font-extrabold text-gray-900">
      Frequently asked questions
    </h2>
    <div class="mt-6 border-t-2 border-gray-100 pt-10">
      <dl class="md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-8">
        <div>
          <div>
            <dt class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">
              Is this secure? What happens to my file?
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2">
              <p class="text-base leading-6 text-gray-500">
              We generate the separated PDF's for you and make them available for download. Your data is never saved on our servers. This project is completely open source. You can
              <a href="https://github.com/or-equals/letter_legal_separator">check out the code here</a>.
              </p>
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-12">
            <dt class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">
               Why is this free?
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2">
              <p class="text-base leading-6 text-gray-500">
                I (Joshua Plicque at Or Equals) built software for the legal field for about four years. I made this to help out a friend. It was fun!
              </p>
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-12">
            <dt class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">
              I have a suggestion or another question!
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2">
              <p class="text-base leading-6 text-gray-500">
                I'd love to hear it! Reach out to me at <a href="mailto:josh@orequals.com">josh@orequals.com</a>
              </p>
            </dd>
          </div>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
